while( buttonChoice != button 2.2 )
    <p> You continue walking. Your feet are growing heavy. </p>

    <button 2.1> Continue walking. </button>
    if (intelligence > 12) # then option 2 is visible
        <button 2.2> Investigate. </button>

# once the user clicks 2. investigate 
<p>You lean in closer to smell the sand. Definitely sugar.</p>

<button 3.1>Continue walking.</button>
