4.3		Algorithm Style


4.3.1		Development Algorithm

The key features of the game include:
•	Frame is adjusted to fit both desktop and mobile view.

•	Backpack object is created as shown on UML diagram 

•	Game cannot be saved and restored later. Upon closing the game, Player will have to start from the beginning at the next opening of the program.

•	Constant addition of content and features in order to increase replay value for the users.



 


